159th Street, west side, north from Evans Road, showing homes that were typical of old Jamaica. 159th Street was formerly Prospect Street, and Evans Road was formerly Catherine Street, a short, crooked thoroughfare. Evans Road is now an appendage to Liberty Avenue, the rest of Catherine Street having
been widened and renamed Liberty Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 30, 1932
